<A>__{angle on a boy, scrawny and filthy, in his early to mid teens. he crouches on the supports of a freeway sign. he wears layers of tattered, over sized clothing. he scrambles quickly down from the sign. at an off ramp, marcus' pace slows as he moves to get off the freeway, when the boy emerges from behind some rubble, holding a handgun in one hand, a lit oil lantern in the other.}
<C>__{boy }
<D>__{whoah, whoah hang on there. got any food?}
