<A>__{marcus hooks his foot around the oil lantern and deftly boots it at the girl. burning oil spills across her leg, she cries out and fumbles the shotgun. marcus tosses the boy at her, the two of them sprawl on the ground, the shotgun falling to one side marcus quickly snatches up the shotgun. using snow, the boy helps the girl extinguish the flames from her clothing. marcus stands over the kids with a gun in each hand. he struggles to control anger, speaks quietly.}
